<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>欢迎加入 My-KM</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .message {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .feature {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding-left: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .feature:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 欢迎加入 My-KM！</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">你好 {{username}}，</p>
            <p class="message">
                恭喜您成功注册 My-KM 个人知识管理系统！
            </p>
            <p class="message">
                我们很高兴能成为您知识管理旅程的伙伴。My-KM 将帮助您更高效地组织、管理和检索您的知识。
            </p>
            <div class="features">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #333;">您现在可以：</p>
                <div class="feature">创建和管理文章</div>
                <div class="feature">组织分类和标签</div>
                <div class="feature">使用 AI 辅助写作和问答</div>
                <div class="feature">随时随地访问您的知识库</div>
            </div>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}" class="button">开始使用</a>
            </div>
            <p class="message">
                如果您有任何问题或建议，欢迎随时联系我们。
            </p>
            <p class="message">
                祝您使用愉快！
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{year}} My-KM. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
